abstract: Former professional tennis player and coach Nick Lindahl pleads guilty in Australia to match-fixing charge related to 2013 tournament.
snippet: Nick Lindahl, a former professional tennis player and coach, pleaded guilty in an Australian court to a charge related to match-fixing related to a game in a minor tournament in 2013.
lead_paragraph: Nick Lindahl, a former professional tennis player and coach, pleaded guilty in an Australian court to a charge related to match-fixing related to a game in a minor tournament in 2013.
